		<p style="margin:0;color:#4c555b;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">For most situations in Lexington, care can begin <strong style="color:#2b2f33;font-weight:600;">within 24 to 48 hours</strong> of your free consultation. Urgent hospital-discharge or post-surgery situations are often started the same day.</p>
	</div>
	<div style="border:1px solid #e7e3dc;border-radius:10px;background:#ffffff;padding:22px 24px;margin:0;">

		<h3 style="font-family:inherit;color:#2b2f33;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin:0 0 10px;line-height:1.4;">Can Comfort Keepers provide Alzheimer&#39;s care at home?</h3>

		<p style="margin:0 0 10px;color:#4c555b;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">Yes. Our caregivers receive specialized training in Alzheimer&#39;s and dementia care, including techniques for redirection, validation, and engagement that help reduce anxiety and preserve dignity.</p>

